{"tid":1083812,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真撚］動真感情","createTime":"2019-03-30T02:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T04:39:18.000Z","uid":44503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b10f5530ac626d358a6cf24e9c6300ea23e2411f","tid":1083812,"uid":44503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"公司最近內部調動 有Team A &amp; Team B<br />\n咁小弟就係Team B既 一個女經理睇既<br />\n咁有個女同事就係Team A 而我同佢關係好似家姐同細佬咁 有好多野都會輔導我 教我<br />\n因為個女同事有兩條𡃁 咁一個就走左 而另一個就同Team A個呀頭唔岩 要調去Team B<br />\n咁男大經理同佢都friend 亦都知我同佢friend 諗住安排我過去跟佢<br />\n但係我以家workload都大 而個女經理就叫我可以幫佢手 （但係叫女同事唔好比咁多野我做）<br />\n而女經理同女同事不嬲都不和<br />\n咁女同事聽到<br />\n而女同事聽到話唔可以比咁多野我做<br />\n之後嬲撚哂Team B既人 <br />\n亦係office冇再咁close 同埋咁傾計<br />\n<br />\n我: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />       女同事:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我唔係嬲你，因為我唔想同Team B 既人有接觸/溝通。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔洗咁呀，你可以照比野我做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔會囉，有人落左order 唔可以比咁多野你做，即係唔洗比啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：......呢幾日同你都變左 好唔慣 唔開心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你會慣架啦，我地原先有感情，以家變到冇感情姐<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知講咩好 就走左<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"16ffe05ed4faae703bdf85a2a4dd39e5fa5e9192","tid":1083812,"uid":44503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:11:09.000Z","msg":"估唔到 被遺棄既感覺咁難受"},{"pid":"01ffdc356dffdc4bffbd85668949ffab87f3970d","tid":1083812,"uid":224107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:43:15.000Z","msg":"返工都會有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /